OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA cloudy
OL,6,Fnight with rain spreading
OL,7,Fnortheastwards and becoming heavy at
OL,8,Ftimes. Rain clearing western
OL,9,FAberdeenshire by morning. Winds
OL,10,Fbecoming strong with coastal gales
OL,11,Fbefore easing later in the night.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FHeavy rain clearing to the
OL,14,Feast in the morning to leave a largely
OL,15,Fdry day with some bright spells and
OL,16,Fjust the odd isolated shower. Light
OL,17,Fwinds strengthening in evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
