OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FCloudy
OL,6,Fwith heavy outbreaks of rain Sunday.
OL,7,FSunny spells and a few showers on
OL,8,FMonday. Dry with sunny spells Tuesday.
OL,9,FStrong winds and risk of gales Sunday,
OL,10,Fthen becoming light.
